text: Starr Walton (born May 13, 1942) is an American alpine skier. She competed in the women's downhill at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:American female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of the United States Category:Alpine skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:People from Yuba City, California
